<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Liên Hệ - BT Beauty Lips</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #fdf2f4; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { color: #ff4d6d; text-align: center; }
        .contact-info { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .info-box { padding: 20px; border-left: 5px solid #ff4d6d; background: #fff0f3; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; }
        #map-container { height: 450px; width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>📍 LIÊN HỆ VỚI CHÚNG TÔI</h1>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Thông tin cửa hàng</h3>
            <p><strong>Địa chỉ:</strong> 123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP. Hồ Chí Minh</p>
            <p><strong>Hotline:</strong> 0900.123.456</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Giờ mở cửa</h3>
            <p>Thứ 2 - Thứ 7: 08:00 - 21:00</p>
            <p>Chủ nhật: 09:00 - 18:00</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</div>
</body>
</html>